name: KibbleSwap
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: KibbleSwap is DogeChain's leading native Decentralized Exchange (DEX). Swap crypto assets native to DogeChain. Farm Liquidity Pairs (LP) and earn $KIB rewards, plus a share of trading fees. Stake $KIB in Single Asset Staking (SAS) pool to earn more $KIB.
